  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2022-07-29",
    "date": "2023-01-09T15:42:57Z",
    "text": "Ending Secrecy About Workplace Harassment Act\n\nThis bill requires every employer that must submit to the Equal Employment Opportunity Commission (EEOC) an Employer Information Report EEO-1 to separately report on an annual basis the number of settlements reached by the employer involving workplace harassment.\n\nThe bill also requires the EEOC and the Government Accountability Office to report information relating to claims of discrimination."
